value.original: You can convert document types (e.g. from Offer to Order or Invoice). The conversion is then reflected in the current type. This processing is initiated by selecting the appropriate Document Action.

row.value:
子类型单据使用不同的自动业务逻辑。当前缺省有32种基础单据类型，其中销售订单有9种子单据，库存订单有3种子单据。

销售订单子类型如下：

报价方案：完成后，不预留库存
报价单：完成后，预留库存
标准订单：完成后，无自动单据生成
仓库订单：完成后，自动生成发货单
赊销订单：完成后，自动生成发货单、发票
预付订单：完成后无动作，付款后自动生成发货单、发票
POS订单：完成后，自动生成发货单、发票、收款单
退货授权：分客户RMA和供应商RMA

仓库单据子类型如下：

盘点单：存货数量变动
内部领用单：存货数量变动
成本调整单：存货金额变动

更多说明参考：http://idempiere_guide_fi.mydoc.io/?t=178385

value.original: The defaults are evaluated in the order of definition, the first not null value becomes the default value of the column. The values are separated by comma or semicolon. a) Literals:. 'Text' or 123 b) Variables - in format @Variable@ - Login e.g. #Date, #AD_Org_ID, #AD_Client_ID - Accounting Schema: e.g. $C_AcctSchema_ID, $C_Calendar_ID - Global defaults: e.g. DateFormat - Window values (all Picks, CheckBoxes, RadioButtons, and DateDoc/DateAcct) c) SQL code with the tag: @SQL=SELECT something AS DefaultValue FROM ... The SQL statement can contain variables. There can be no other value other than the SQL statement. The default is only evaluated, if no user preference is defined. Default definitions are ignored for record columns as Key, Parent, Client as well as Buttons.

row.value:

c) SQL代码：@SQL=SELECT xxx AS DefaultValue FROM ....@，SQL语句可以包含变量
缺省值只有在用户偏好值为空时起效，如果列为主键、父键、实体或者按钮，缺省值将忽略。

value.original:
format := {expression} [{logic} {expression}]
expression := @{context}@{operand}{value} or @{context}@{operand}{value}
logic := {|}|{&}
context := any global or window context
value := strings or numbers
logic operators := AND or OR with the previous result from left to right
operand := eq{=}, gt{>}, le{<}, not{~^!}
Examples:
@AD_Table_ID@=14 | @Language@!GERGER
@PriceLimit@>10 | @PriceList@>@PriceActual@
@Name@>J
Strings may be in single quotes (optional)

The document number is usually automatically generated by the system and determined by the document type of the document. If the document is not saved, the preliminary number is displayed in "<>".
If the document type of your document has no automatic document sequence defined, the field is empty if you create a new document. This is for documents which usually have an external number (like vendor invoice). If you leave the field empty, the system will generate a document number for you. value.original: There are two methods of making records unavailable in the system: One is to delete the record, the other is to de-activate the record. A de-activated record is not available for selection, but available for reports. There are two reasons for de-activating and not deleting records: (1) The system requires the record for audit purposes. (2) The record is referenced by other records. E.g., you cannot delete a Business Partner, if there are invoices for this partner record existing. You de-activate the Business Partner and prevent that this record is used for future entries.

value.original:
The SO Sub Type indicates the type of sales order this document refers to. This field only appears when the Document Base Type is Sales Order. The selection made here will determine which documents will be generated when an order is processed and which documents must be generated manually or in batches.
The following outlines this process.
SO Sub Type of Standard Order will generate just the Order document when the order is processed.
The Delivery Note, Invoice and Receipt must be generated via other processes.
SO Sub Type of Warehouse Order will generate the Order and Delivery Note.
The Invoice and Receipt must be generated via other processes.
SO Sub Type of Credit Order will generate the Order, Delivery Note and Invoice.
The Receipt must be generated via other processes.
SO Sub Type of POS (Point of Sale) will generate all document

value.original: The Not Invoiced Receipts account indicates the account used for recording receipts for materials that have not yet been invoiced.

row.value:
也叫“应付账款->应付暂估”，借方余额表示已到票的未税暂估金额，贷方表示已到货的未税暂估金额。
通常采购发票会晚于收货时间，通常该科目会冲回处理。
如果企业不允许“票到货未到”情况，也可不使用“材料采购 (已到票)”账户，将其设置成“应付账款 (未开票)”即可。
实际业务中，票货到达情况分为3种：
1. 票到货到，当期完成
2. 票到货未到
3. 货到票未到
前2种，会计收到发票后，不做任何处理，直到收货后才开始先录入收货单、然后录入发票，最后确认分配，形成真正的应付账款。
第3种情况，即国内常见“暂估”处理。

value.original: The Relative Priority indicates the location to pick from first if an product is stored in more than one location. (100 = highest priority, 0 = lowest). For outgoing shipments, the location is picked with the highest priority where the entire quantity can be shipped from. If there is no location, the location with the highest priority is used. The Priority is ignored for products with Guarantee Date (always the oldest first) or if a specific instance is selected. Incoming receipts are stored at the location with the highest priority, if not explicitly selected.

row.value:
当非实例属性产品存在于多个库位时，该数值决定了物品被挑库出货的优先级别。100表示最高，0表示最低。
对于发货，最高优先的库位会被选择发出，直到数量用尽。但是对于有保质期的产品或者实例属性产品的出货，不考虑该优先级别
对于收货，如果不指明具体库位，也会被收到最高优先级别的库位。

请求创建后，请求接收人将会在工作台收“待办事宜”窗口看到请求数量变化。到期后是否发送电子邮件通知由请求类型定义，需要电子邮件服务器支持。

value.original: The defaults are evaluated in the order of definition, the first not null value becomes the default value of the column. The values are separated by comma or semicolon. a) Literals:. 'Text' or 123 b) Variables - in format @Variable@ - Login e.g. #Date, #AD_Org_ID, #AD_Client_ID - Accounting Schema: e.g. $C_AcctSchema_ID, $C_Calendar_ID - Global defaults: e.g. DateFormat - Window values (all Picks, CheckBoxes, RadioButtons, and DateDoc/DateAcct) c) SQL code with the tag: @SQL=SELECT something AS DefaultValue FROM ... The SQL statement can contain variables. There can be no other value other than the SQL statement. The default is only evaluated, if no user preference is defined. Default definitions are ignored for record columns as Key, Parent, Client as well as Buttons.

row.value:
缺省值支持多级候选，直到符合第一个非空值。
a) 常量：‘文本’或者123
b) 变量：@变量@，变量比如#Date, #AD_Org_ID, $C_AcctSchema, DateFormat, 窗口变量等等
c) SQL代码：@SQL=SELECT xxx AS DefaultValue FROM ....@，SQL语句可以包含变量
缺省值只有在用户偏好值为空时起效，如果列为主键、父键、实体或者按钮，缺省值将忽略。

Logic to determine Workflow Start - If true, a workflow process is started for the document

row.value: 决定工作流启动的逻辑 - 如果为真， 就会启动单据的工作流流程

value.original: You can enter simple logic using variables like @Created@=@Updated@, which fires, when a record is created. If you need to evaluate also values of other records, you need to use SQL logic and need to prefix this logic with "SQL=". Example: start a Order verify workflow, when a business partner ordered something and is over the credit limit "SQL=EXISTS (SELECT * FROM C_BPartner bp WHERE C_Order. C_BPartner_ID=bp. C_BPartner_ID AND SO_CreditUsed > SO_CreditLimit)". Note that the SQL based logic checks for duplicate workflows (i.e. a workflow is started only once per record).

row.value:
借方余额表示未匹配入库的到票金额，贷方余额表示已匹配入库的发票金额。
业务完成后，该账户期末余额应该为零。通常企业不允许“票到货未到”，到票时间一般会晚于入库时间。会计分录如下：
收货：
借：库存资产
贷：应付账款>未开票

收票：
借：材料采购>已到票
贷：应付账款

发票匹配收货：
借：应付账款>未开票
贷：材料采购>已到票

【准则解释】
原企业会计制度设置“物资采购”会计科目核算企业购入材料、商品等的采购成本，无论企业采用实际成本还是采用计划成本进行材料、商品的日常核算，均可以使用本科目。1.对于工业企业可以将本科目改为“材料采购”科目来进行材料的日常核算.。
2.对于商品流通企业因采购商品而在期末发生的在途商品，以及采用实际成本核算材料、商品的企业,可以将本科目改为“在途物资”科目核算.。
3.新准则似乎取消了“物资采购”科目的使用，并明确区分了“材料采购”和“在途物资”两个科目的核算内容。其中，“材料采购”科目核算企业采用计划成本进行材料日常核算而购入材料的采购成本，本科目应当按照供应单位和物资品种进行明细核算；“在途物资”科目核算企业采用实际成本（或进价）进行材料（或商品）日常核算，货款已付尚未验收入库的购入材料或商品的采购成本，本科目应当按照供应单位进行明细核算。
“物资采购”和“材料采购”俩科目核算内容实际一样,只是科目描述不同而已。
对于尚未收到发票账单的收料凭证，应按计划成本暂估入账，借记“原材料”、“周转材料”等科目，贷记“应付账款——暂估应付账款”科目，下期初做相反分录予以冲回。下期收到发票账单的收料凭证，借记本科目，贷记“银行存款”、“应付账款”、“应付票据”等科目。涉及增值税进项税额的，还应进行相应的处理。

value.original:
The Rate Variance is used in Standard Costing. It reflects the difference between the Standard Cost Rates and The Cost Rates of Manufacturing Order.
If you change the Standard Rates then this variance is generate.

row.value:
反映标准工费与生产工单的实际工费的差额。生产工单的成本通常包含：材料、人工、变动费用。此处仅记录人工工费部分。比如生产了10件产品：
标准单件工时=1小时/件，标准工资率 = 10 元/小时 ；
实际工资率 = 15 元/小时，实际使用工时 = 8小时 ；

计算方法一：分2个维度来统计差异
1. 直接人工成本差异= ( 实际工资率 - 标准工资率 ) x 实际工时 = ( 15- 10 ) * 8 = 40元
2. 直接效率成本差异= ( 实际工时 - 标准单件工时*实际产量 ) x 标准工资率 = （8 - 1*10）x 10 = -20元
差异= 项1 + 项2 = 40 - 20 = 20 元 （人贵效率不咋的）
计算方法二：按单件成本来统计差异
差异 = （实际单件成本 - 标准单件成本）x 实际产量 = ( 15x8/10 - 1x10 ) x10 = ( 12 -10 ) x 10 = 20 元 （反正贵了）

value.original: Internal Document sequence number of the document

row.value: Internal Document sequence number of the document

value.original:
The document number is usually automatically generated by the system and determined by the document type of the document. If the document is not saved, the preliminary number is displayed in "<>".
If the document type of your document has no automatic document sequence defined, the field is empty if you create a new document. This is for documents which usually have an external number (like vendor invoice). If you leave the field empty, the system will generate a document number for you. The document sequence used for this fallback number is defined in the "Maintain Sequence" window with the name "DocumentNo_<TableName>", where TableName is the actual name of the table (e.g. C_Order).

row.value: Internal Document sequence number of the document
